{"tid":2436582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳盂達設靈 周星馳現身致祭","createTime":"2021-03-07T08:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T05:30:42.000Z","uid":39539,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"23f0683142c3a96161cef223835de56819db1508","tid":2436582,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"外界一直在關注周星馳會否親到靈堂弔唁，終於星爺於下午4點15分抵達，送昔日的黃金搭檔最後一程。星爺和胞姊周文姬一同到達殯儀館，兩人均身穿黑素服，神情肅穆現身時，引起一陣騷動，而愛低調的星爺更和姊姊分開門口進入殯儀館。兩人在靈堂內逗留約9分鐘後，周星馳和家姐一齊離開，家姐行先星爺殿後。在場傳媒問星爺與達哥有甚麼點滴，星爺揮一揮手沒有回應，然後便坐七人車離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZDMVs8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZDMVs8.png&h=ed80487f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4e37ac5df97f1050c795e2a18e05dee643a0f2f2","tid":2436582,"uid":215089,"like":8,"dislike":22,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n請專注關注被捕手足"},{"pid":"ae65fe1821957a4f1b05d1b0e67cec0c4ae90940","tid":2436582,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4e37ac5df97f1050c795e2a18e05dee643a0f2f2","tid":2436582,"uid":215089,"like":8,"dislike":22,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n請專注關注被捕手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"738d0892dfbfa90598dd808de30466637ce9fe21","tid":2436582,"uid":10520,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4e37ac5df97f1050c795e2a18e05dee643a0f2f2","tid":2436582,"uid":215089,"like":8,"dislike":22,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n請專注關注被捕手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:05:01.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"1d96d4f2f7f05a00ae7d0b2504bcf06181624379","tid":2436582,"uid":74918,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4e37ac5df97f1050c795e2a18e05dee643a0f2f2","tid":2436582,"uid":215089,"like":8,"dislike":22,"score":-14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T09:00:56.000Z","msg":"冇人想知呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n請專注關注